data.text: @BonBon_nie *Texts back ,”Meet me at my mansion and make sure he’s not following. I think he’s a skin walker .”*She texted back immediately before heading to the back yard to wait on her*
@HellsLastKnight What? *I was so confused about her text so I replied as soon as I could* Abaddon, I'm okay but how is that possible? I'll meet you!
